Package com.cafean.client.ui.navigator

Interface NavigatorModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    javax.swing.tree.TreeModel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MiniNavigatorTreeModel, NavigatorTreeModel
    public interface NavigatorModel
extends javax.swing.tree.TreeModel
    An interface representing a NavigatorTreeModel or a MiniNavigatorTreeModel. This is used to share code between the singleton navigator and the mini-navigator used for specific component properties.

        NavigatorNode componentAdded​(AbstractComponent comp,
                             AbstractModel current)
        Notifies this Navigator that the given component was added to the given Category. Adds a node for the component to the appropriate CategoryNode and fires the appropriate events.
        Parameters:
        comp - the AbstractComponent added
        current - the AbstractModel containing the added component
